{"tid":832084,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［連登有愛］求求巴絲收留就狗仔","createTime":"2018-09-22T13:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T18:57:44.000Z","uid":201547,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f788a2b5426860538e9e9c393d2da3cf780e60ba","tid":832084,"uid":201547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"幫朋友出po<br />\n<br />\n事源我有朋友個親戚走去領養狗仔，但養唔夠兩個月就唔想養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我朋友家姐唔想隻狗仔送去狗場俾其他大狗蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以就暫時養住隻狗仔先，但係我朋友屋企人又唔畀養狗，只好上嚟問下有冇巴絲願意收留下呢隻狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/212838_84f2e99802ea345b9569e65113b1c0fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F212838_84f2e99802ea345b9569e65113b1c0fa.png&h=a935a03a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/212840_f6c3e8729b421548fdf22510e28c6286.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F212840_f6c3e8729b421548fdf22510e28c6286.png&h=527f5208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻狗仔叫小吉<br />\n8個月大 <br />\n識用training pad<br />\n性格痴人，細膽，怕羞，乖巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現暫託喺我朋友屋企<br />\n希望有熱心巴絲肯收留佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意請聯絡：9206 3105"},{"pid":"84f21615c3890b62f9e0717052dc0cb028f3f834","tid":832084,"uid":201547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"標題打錯 *隻 狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15237ead0de2371c071ab588a7463afdb3888deb","tid":832084,"uid":29689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"你朋友（即是你）仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef006a02b0f07310cf80cb0d5b074dea00e2446f","tid":832084,"uid":84524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"你的朋友就是你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n棄養全家仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78516633c0d5b8b23e24cbf851f59c8fa03b9d53","tid":832084,"uid":201547,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:09:13.000Z","msg":"大家唔好錯重點，重點係隻狗仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e171f05fa29b2edf78f6056458bc3a5c4a8b714","tid":832084,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5984c53a16513d618cbb1e3be6a76698bc3472b6","tid":832084,"uid":201547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e171f05fa29b2edf78f6056458bc3a5c4a8b714","tid":832084,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609a81788c924da864a191daa2f7008e6a9820c4","tid":832084,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"我要 狗肉煲我黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afef21c206137cebaf13987c84984ec0d11e4e6a","tid":832084,"uid":201547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609a81788c924da864a191daa2f7008e6a9820c4","tid":832084,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"我要 狗肉煲我黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces